# Cloudflare Pages headers
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/
#
# Everything revalidates on every request (max-age=0) rather than
# following website/_headers' longer /assets/* cache - this repo is
# still under active, rapid iteration, and a stale cached CSS/JS file
# silently masking a just-shipped fix is worse than the small
# performance cost of always revalidating. Worth revisiting once
# changes slow down.

/*
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
